v></div><div class="mantine-Carousel-slide mantine-1w44auj"><div class="relative block h-[320px] sm:h-[540px]"><a href="/compass/your-guide-to-the-silk-road-by-rail"><img alt="Orient Silk Road Express" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="z-0 object-cover" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 1280px) 50vw, 33vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Ffe314063288592b49751e7e64b3c7022641382ac-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=1440&amp;q=65 1440w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Ffe314063288592b49751e7e64b3c7022641382ac-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=1920&amp;q=65 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Ffe314063288592b49751e7e64b3c7022641382ac-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=2048&amp;q=65 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Ffe314063288592b49751e7e64b3c7022641382ac-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=3840&amp;q=65 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Ffe314063288592b49751e7e64b3c7022641382ac-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=3840&amp;q=65"/><div class="absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/95 via-black/40 to-transparent"></div><div class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-0 z-20 px-4 py-5 sm:px-6 sm:py-12"><h2 class="text-center text-white">Your guide to the Silk Road by rail</h2></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-20 text-center text-white"><div class="mb-3 px-4 sm:mb-7 [&amp;&gt;p]:line-clamp-4 [&amp;&gt;p]:text-s"><p>When it comes to holidays, the Stans of Central Asia are often overlooked. Yet the curious traveller will find these crossroad countries every bit as rich in history, culture and nature as anywhere to their east or west.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><a href="/compass/your-guide-to-the-silk-road-by-rail" class="border-b border-white w-fit font-bold">READ MORE</a></p></div></div></a></div></div><div class="mantine-Carousel-slide mantine-1w44auj"><div class="relative block h-[320px] sm:h-[540px]"><a href="/compass/highlights-of-chile-travel-guide-where-to-go-and-what-to-do"><img alt="Torres del Paine National Park" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="z-0 object-cover" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 1280px) 50vw, 33vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Fdb17f89cabf07f96a3de1e02301530b43061a033-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=1440&amp;q=65 1440w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Fdb17f89cabf07f96a3de1e02301530b43061a033-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=1920&amp;q=65 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Fdb17f89cabf07f96a3de1e02301530b43061a033-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=2048&amp;q=65 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Fdb17f89cabf07f96a3de1e02301530b43061a033-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=3840&amp;q=65 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2Fdb17f89cabf07f96a3de1e02301530b43061a033-2560x1440.jpg%3Frect%3D704%2C0%2C1152%2C1440%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=3840&amp;q=65"/><div class="absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/95 via-black/40 to-transparent"></div><div class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-0 z-20 px-4 py-5 sm:px-6 sm:py-12"><h2 class="text-center text-white">Highlights of Chile travel guide: where to go and what to do</h2></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-20 text-center text-white"><div class="mb-3 px-4 sm:mb-7 [&amp;&gt;p]:line-clamp-4 [&amp;&gt;p]:text-s"><p>Stretching 4,300km from the rugged and windswept wilds of Patagonia to the otherworldly landscapes of the Atacama Desert, Chile is a land of diversity.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><a href="/compass/highlights-of-chile-travel-guide-where-to-go-and-what-to-do" class="border-b border-white w-fit font-bold">READ MORE</a></p></div></div></a></div></div><div class="mantine-Carousel-slide mantine-1w44auj"><div class="relative block h-[320px] sm:h-[540px]"><a href="/compass/why-barolo-is-italys-king-of-wines"><img alt="Wine region" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="z-0 object-cover" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 1280px) 50vw, 33vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2F7b77491b518fc1c4c7a9b907c9f147d9a8bf4036-5251x2954.jpg%3Frect%3D1445%2C0%2C2363%2C2954%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=1440&amp;q=65 1440w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2F7b77491b518fc1c4c7a9b907c9f147d9a8bf4036-5251x2954.jpg%3Frect%3D1445%2C0%2C2363%2C2954%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=1920&amp;q=65 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2F7b77491b518fc1c4c7a9b907c9f147d9a8bf4036-5251x2954.jpg%3Frect%3D1445%2C0%2C2363%2C2954%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=2048&amp;q=65 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2F7b77491b518fc1c4c7a9b907c9f147d9a8bf4036-5251x2954.jpg%3Frect%3D1445%2C0%2C2363%2C2954%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=3840&amp;q=65 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.coxandkingstravel.com%2Fimages%2Fztdma7t1%2Fproduction%2F7b77491b518fc1c4c7a9b907c9f147d9a8bf4036-5251x2954.jpg%3Frect%3D1445%2C0%2C2363%2C2954%26w%3D800%26h%3D1000%26fit%3Dmax%26auto%3Dformat&amp;w=3840&amp;q=65"/><div class="absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/95 via-black/40 to-transparent"></div><div class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-0 z-20 px-4 py-5 sm:px-6 sm:py-12"><h2 class="text-center text-white">Why Barolo is Italy’s King of Wines</h2></div><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-20 text-center text-white"><div class="mb-3 px-4 sm:mb-7 [&amp;&gt;p]:line-clamp-4 [&amp;&gt;p]:text-s"><p>Italian chef and gastronomic guide Valentina Harris reveals the noble heritage of Barolo, Piedmont’s most famous wine.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><a href="/compass/why-barolo-is-italys-king-of-wines" class="border-b border-white w-fit font-bold">READ MORE</a></p></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="mantine-4ny9bc mantine-Carousel-controls"><button class="mantine-UnstyledButton-root mantine-Carousel-control mantine-zxfiso" type="button" data-inactive="true" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex aspect-[1] h-[37px] w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full border-[1px] border-black/15 bg-white"><span class="i-icon i-icon-arrow-left"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><path d="M5.79889 24H41.7989" stroke="#000" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M17.7988 36L5.79883 24L17.7988 12" stroke="#000" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></div></button><button class="mantine-UnstyledButton-root mantine-Carousel-control mantine-zxfiso" type="button" data-inactive="true" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex aspect-[1] h-[37px] w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full border-[1px] border-black/15 bg-white"><span class="i-icon i-icon-arrow-right"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><path d="M41.9999 24H5.99994" stroke="#000" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M30 12L42 24L30 36" stroke="#000" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></div></button></div></div></div></section><div id="trust-pilot" class="trustpilot-widget bg-white pb-[60px] pt-[60px] constrain-container mt-[60px] py-[60px]" data-locale="en-GB" data-template-id="53aa8912dec7e10d38f59f36" data-businessunit-id="59cccc580000ff0005ac4238" data-style-height="140px" data-style-width="100%" data-token="65d9a3ac-33df-49df-8a74-a98fe72299e4" data-stars="5" data-review-languages="en" data-font-family="Open Sans"><a href="https://uk.trustpilot.com/review/coxandkings.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Trustpilot</a></div><section id="carousel-info-cards" class="bg-[#F1F4F8]"><div class="constrain-container py-12"><h2 class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-[90%] text-center text-[#001E3B] sm:max-w-full">Why choose Cox &amp; Kings</h2><div class="mantine-Carousel-root info-card-carousel-container relative mantine-12sbrde"><div class="mantine-1inun54 mantine-Carousel-viewport"><div class="mantine-1okoifh mantine-Carousel-container"><div class="mantine-Carousel-slide mantine-1bq3zt6"><div class="mantine-Paper-root mantine-Card-root flex h-full flex-col items-center p-6 text-center sm:min-h-full mantine-17yq1a2"><div class="mb-4 flex w-full justify-center text-gray-500 sm:justify-start"><span></span></div><div class="text-center text-m sm:text-left"><p><strong>Genuinely small groups</strong></p><p></p><p>Small groups promise a more personal touring experience. That’s why Cox &amp; Kings maintains a maximum group size of 18 guests on most tours, and an average of just 14.</p></div></div></div><div class="mantine-Carousel-slide mantine-1bq3zt6"><div class="mantine-Paper-root mantine-Card-root flex h-full flex-col items-center p-6 text-center sm:min-h-full mantine-17yq1a2"><div class="mb-4 flex w-full justify-center text-gray-500 sm:justify-start"><span></span></div><div class="text-center text-m sm:text-left"><p><strong>Worldwide support</strong></p><p></p><p>Enjoy round-the-clock support – in person, over the phone and online. This is made possible by our well-travelled staff and unrivalled network of offices in destinations across the world.</p></div></div></div><div class="mantine-Carousel-slide mantine-1bq3zt6"><div class="mantine-Paper-root mantine-Card-root flex h-full flex-col items-center p-6 text-center sm:min-h-full mantine-17yq1a2"><div class="mb-4 flex w-full justify-center text-gray-500 sm:justify-start"><span></span></div><div class="text-center text-m sm:text-left"><p><strong>Experts since 1758</strong></p><p></p><p>Cox &amp; Kings is a name you can trust. We’ve been helping the curious traveller explore for more than 265 years – longer than any other travel company.</p></div></div></div><div class="mantine-Carousel-slide mantine-1bq3zt6"><div class="mantine-Paper-root mantine-Card-root flex h-full flex-col items-center p-6 text-center sm:min-h-full mantine-17yq1a2"><div class="mb-4 flex w-full justify-center text-gray-500 sm:justify-start"><span></span></div><div class="text-center text-m sm:text-left"><p><strong>Tailored to you</strong></p><p></p><p>Cox &amp; Kings has been organising tailor-made holidays for generations. Let our specialists arrange an itinerary exactly tailored to your needs – no matter how complex or unique they may be.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><!--$?--><template id="B:1"></template><!--/$--></div></main><!--$?--><template id="B:2"></template><!--/$--></div><noscript>
