 leisure or further explore Machu Picchu (purchase ticket at time of booking). Return to Cuzco by rail and transfer to the Palacio del Inka, a Luxury Collection Hotel for 2 nights.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Cuzco\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYqrX\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_248986\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":2990,\"cityIDTo\":4699,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Machu Picchu\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Cuzco\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247735\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Train\"}],\"meals\":[\"breakfast\"]},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYqy9\",\"accommodations\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYr84\",\"accommodation\":{\"_ref\":\"accommodation-33131\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"options\":[158606]}],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYr1S\",\"city\":\"Cusco Region\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_region_245851\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":14,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eHalf-day tour of the Inca capital including the San Blas district, the cathedral and the extraordinary Temple of the Sun at Coricancha. Afternoon is at leisure or take an optional excursion to the Pre-Columbian Art Museum or the ruins of Sacsayhuamán, before your farewell dinner that evening\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Cuzco\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYr4l\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247735\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":4699,\"cityIDTo\":4699,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Cuzco\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Cuzco\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247735\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"meals\":[\"breakfast\",\"dinner\"]},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYrBN\",\"day\":14.1,\"dayTitle\":\"Transfer: Cuzco to Lima\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYrEg\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247735\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":4699,\"cityIDTo\