"Lucide\",\"downloadUrl\":\"https://api.iconify.design/lucide:sparkle.svg?width=20\u0026height=20\u0026download=1\",\"flip\":\"\",\"hFlip\":false,\"iconName\":\"sparkle\",\"license\":{\"name\":\"ISC\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide/blob/main/LICENSE\"},\"palette\":false,\"rotate\":0,\"size\":{\"height\":20,\"width\":20},\"url\":\"https://api.iconify.design/lucide:sparkle.svg?width=20\u0026height=20\",\"vFlip\":false}},\"name\":\"Generic\",\"position\":2},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYgpv\",\"description\":\"\u003cp\u003eSpot majestic condors in Colca Canyon\u003c/p\u003e\",\"icon\":{\"_type\":\"icon.manager\",\"icon\":\"lucide:sparkle\",\"metadata\":{\"author\":{\"name\":\"Lucide Contributors\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide\"},\"collectionId\":\"lucide\",\"collectionName\":\"Lucide\",\"downloadUrl\":\"https://api.iconify.design/lucide:sparkle.svg?width=20\u0026height=20\u0026download=1\",\"flip\":\"\",\"hFlip\":false,\"iconName\":\"sparkle\",\"license\":{\"name\":\"ISC\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide/blob/main/LICENSE\"},\"palette\":false,\"rotate\":0,\"size\":{\"height\":20,\"width\":20},\"url\":\"https://api.iconify.design/lucide:sparkle.svg?width=20\u0026height=20\",\"vFlip\":false}},\"name\":\"Generic\",\"position\":3},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYgtE\",\"description\":\"\u003cp\u003eScenic rail journey across the altiplano aboard the stylish Titicaca train\u003c/p\u003e\",\"icon\":{\"_type\":\"icon.manager\",\"icon\":\"lucide:sparkle\",\"metadata\":{\"author\":{\"name\":\"Lucide Contributors\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide\"},\"collectionId\":\"lucide\",\"collectionName\":\"Lucide\",\"downloadUrl\":\"https://api.iconify.design/lucide:sparkle.svg?width=20\u0026height=20\u0026download=1\",\"flip\":\"\",\"hFlip\":false,\"iconName\":\"sparkle\",\"license\":{\"name\":\"ISC\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide/blob/main/LICENSE\"},\"palette\":false,\"rotate\":0,\"size\":{\"height\":20,\"width\":20},\"url\":\"https://api.iconify.design/lucide:sparkle.svg?width=20\u0026height=20\",\"vFlip\":false}},\"name\":\"Generic\",\"position\":4}],\"includesInternalAir\":false,\"initialPrices\":[],\"journeyDetails\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYh9l\",\"description\":\"This itinerary can be taken privately on a date that suits you. Alternatively, it can be tailored to your exact requirements. So, should you want to spend longer in a particular location, or add another experience or destination, we can make all the arrangements for you. Please contact our travel specialists for guideline prices.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Private \u0026 tailor-made travel\"},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhD4\",\"description\":\"Where a tour date shows ‘Guaranteed departure', this tour is guaranteed to run. For all other departure dates, once the minimum number of people booked has been reached, this tour is also guaranteed to run. Our sales consultants will be able to advise how many people are booked for your chosen date at the time of enquiry, giving you the confidence to book safe in the knowledge your tour will go ahead.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Guaranteed departures\"},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhGN\",\"description\":\"Unless otherwise stated, the tour prices and upgrade supplements are all per person in Euros, based on two people sharing a twin/double room. The online price is a guideline price.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":false,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":false,\"us\":false,\"world\":false},\"title\":\"Dates and Prices\"},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhJg\",\"description\":\"Unless otherwise stated, the tour prices and upgrade supplements are all per person in pound sterling, based on two people sharing a twin/double room. The online price is a guideline price; your final quote may differ due to flight availability, and you may be asked to pay a flight supplement.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":false,\"eu\":false,\"gb\":true,\"us\":false,\"world\":false},\"title\":\"Dates and Prices\"},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhMz\",\"description\":\"These are our most comfortable tours and will usually feature 5-star deluxe accommodation throughout\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Luxury Tour\"},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhQI\",\"description\":\"Medium pace, some  longer travel days, with uneven terrain and  longer walks requiring good fitness  and mobility.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Moderate activity level\"},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhTb\",\"description\":\"The order of the itinerary allows  gradual adjustment to the altitude, while  taking in the major sights of Peru. There are  some early morning starts and long drives.  Currently all departures will fly to Peru via  Amsterdam.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Itinerary\"},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhWu\",\"description\":\"Unless otherwise stated, the tour prices and upgrade supplements are all per person in Australian Dollars, based on two people sharing a twin/double room. The online price is a guideline price.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":false,\"gb\":false,\"us\":false,\"world\":false},\"title\":\"Dates and Prices\"},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhaD\",\"description\":\"Unless otherwise stated, the tour prices and upgrade supplements are all per person in United States Dollars, based on two people sharing a twin/double room. The online price is a guideline price.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":false,\"eu\":false,\"gb\":false,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Dates and Prices\"}],\"lengthDays\":16,\"locations\":0,\"locationsType\":null,\"lowestPreviousPrices\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYgW5\",\"currency\":\"AUD\",\"price\":8295},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYgZO\",\"currency\":\"USD\",\"price\":7295},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYgch\",\"currency\":\"GBP\",\"price\":4295},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYgg0\",\"currency\":\"EUR\",\"price\":3295}],\"lowestPrices\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhdW\",\"currency\":\"AUD\",\"price\":8095},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhgp\",\"currency\":\"USD\",\"price\":7170},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhk8\",\"currency\":\"GBP\",\"price\":4095},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYhnR\",\"currency\":\"EUR\",\"price\":3195}],\"map\":\"https://stcontentprodeastus001.blob.core.windows.net/ecm/Renderings/434/P105512.svg\",\"mapJson\":\"$2f\",\"maxDiscounts\":[{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYgwX\",\"currency\":\"AUD\",\"price\":200},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYgzq\",\"currency\":\"USD\",\"price\":125},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYh39\",\"currency\":\"GBP\",\"price\":200},{\"_key\":\"bNKZj4hxI3qs1eUORvYh6S\",\"currency\":\"EUR\",\"price\":100}],\"offerFlags\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"offers\":[],\"overviewText\":\"Machu Picchu is perhaps the most breathtaking archaeological site in the world. Yet Peru also offers a wealth of other magnificent ancient, colonial and scenic sights. Staying in good hotels with great character and with some free time to relax, this tour reveals Peru’s many wonders, including Cuzco and Arequipa, the Colca Canyon, Lake Titicaca and, of course, Machu Picchu.\",\"packageTypeId\":4,\"people\":[],\"slug\":{\"_type\":\"slug\",\"current\":\"small-group-tour/train-to-machu-picchu-luxury\"},\"subType\":\"Small Group Tour\",\"tags\":[],\"title\":\"Train to Machu Picchu (Luxury)\",\"type\":\"Seat in Bus Brochure Tour\",\"year\":2026},{\"AkDestinationId\":245403,\"_createdAt\":\"2025-09-23T22:49:45Z\",\"_id\":\"journeys-package-105431\",\"_rev\":\"YPysR8z5veAiGoP5KUR9FU\",\"_type\":\"journeys\",\"_updatedAt\":\"2026-03-04T03:45:33Z\",\"activityLevel\":\"Active\",\"advantages\":[{\"_key\":\"NSXr7tAZasA1qyCnhRFYoM\",\"description\":\"\u003cp