under your own arrangements. Transfer to Syracuse and stay at Grande Albergo Alfeo (or similar) for 2 nights. Enjoy a welcome drink. \u003cem\u003eOur travel specialists will be delighted to assist with flight arrangements if required.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":true,\"dayTitle\":\"Fly to Catania - Syracuse\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunb7Q\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247455\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":307,\"cityIDTo\":3348,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Catania\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Syracuse\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250515\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbHu\",\"accommodations\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbXd\",\"accommodation\":{\"_ref\":\"accommodation-36285\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"options\":[157652]}],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbN9\",\"city\":\"Syracuse\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250515\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":1,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eFly from London (regional connections available) to Catania with British Airways. Transfer to Syracuse and stay at Grande Albergo Alfeo (or similar) for 2 nights. Enjoy a welcome drink.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Arrive Catania\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbSO\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247455\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":307,\"cityIDTo\":3348,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Catania\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Syracuse\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250515\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbcs\",\"day\":1.1,\"dayTitle\":\"Transfer: Syracuse to Catania\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbi7\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250515\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":3348,\"cityIDTo\":307,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Syracuse\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Catania\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247455\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbnM\",\"accommodations\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunc35\",\"accommodation\":{\"_ref\":\"accommodation-36285\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"options\":[157652]}],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbsb\",\"city\":\"Syracuse\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250515\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":2,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eTour Syracuse, including the Greek theatre, considered one of the most important examples of its kind; the Ear of Dionysius limestone cave; and Ortygia island. Continue to the UNESCO-listed city of Noto, renowned for its magnificent baroque architecture.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Syracuse - Noto\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunbxq\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250515\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":3348,\"cityIDTo\":307,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Syracuse\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Catania\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247455\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}],\"meals\":[\"breakfast\"]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunc8K\",\"day\":2.1,\"dayTitle\":\"Transfer: Catania to Cefalu\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncDZ\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247455\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":307,\"cityIDTo\":3722,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Catania\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Cefalu\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_254386\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncIo\",\"accommodations\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncYX\",\"accommodation\":{\"_ref\":\"accommodation-12011\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"options\":[157626]}],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncO3\",\"city\":\"Palermo, Sicily\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_249614\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":3,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eThis morning, drive to Catania to view the cathedral and Piazza Stesicoro. Continue to Cefalù to visit the Norman cathedral with its exquisite mosaics. Next, travel to Palermo and stay 2 nights at the Hotel Piazza Borsa (or similar).\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Catania - Cefalù - Palermo\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncTI\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247455\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":307,\"cityIDTo\":3722,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Catania\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Cefalu\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_254386\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}],\"meals\":[\"breakfast\"]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncdm\",\"day\":3.1,\"dayTitle\":\"Transfer: Cefalu to Palermo\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncj1\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_254386\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":3722,\"cityIDTo\":965,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Cefalu\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Palermo\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_249614\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncoG\",\"accommodations\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuncyk\",\"accommodation\":{\"_ref\":\"accommodation-12011\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"options\":[157626]}],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUund3z\",\"city\":\"Palermo, Sicily\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_249614\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":4,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eThis morning, drive to Monreale to visit the Norman cathedral, founded in 1172 and considered a leading example of Norman-Arab architecture. Return to Palermo for a city tour including the magnificent Arab-Norman cathedral; the Palatine Chapel, located within the Norman palace and covered in Byzantine influenced mosaics; and the historic old town. During an afternoon street-food experience and light tasting lunch learn how Palermitan cuisine has been shaped by the region's history.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Palermo - Monreale\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunctV\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_254386\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":3722,\"cityIDTo\":965,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Cefalu\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Palermo\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_249614\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}],\"meals\":[\"breakfast\",\"lunch\"]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUund9E\",\"day\":4.1,\"dayTitle\":\"Transfer: Palermo to Erice\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundET\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_249614\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":965,\"cityIDTo\":6007,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Palermo\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Erice\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247937\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundJi\",\"accommodations\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundZR\",\"accommodation\":{\"_ref\":\"accommodation-32201\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"options\":[157626]}],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundOx\",\"city\":\"Agrigento\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_246858\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":5,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eMorning visit to the Archaeological Park of Segesta where you see one of Sicily’s best preserved Doric temples. Proceed to the town of Erice with its imposing fortified walls overlooking the city of Trapani. Stop at Grammatico, the world-famous pastry shop, for some marzipan and biscuit tasting. Drive to Agrigento and stay overnight at the Hotel Colleverde Park (or similar).\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Segesta - Erice - Agrigento\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundUC\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_249614\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":965,\"cityIDTo\":6007,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Palermo\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Erice\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247937\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}],\"meals\":[\"breakfast\"]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundeg\",\"day\":5.1,\"dayTitle\":\"Transfer: Erice to Agrigento\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundjv\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247937\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":6007,\"cityIDTo\":2455,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Erice\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Agrigento\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_246858\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundpA\",\"accommodations\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUune4t\",\"accommodation\":{\"_ref\":\"accommodation-32271\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"options\":[185182]}],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunduP\",\"city\":\"Taormina\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250552\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":6,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eMorning visit to the Valley of the Temples, one of the world's most impressive ancient Greek sites. Afternoon drive to the elegant resort town of Taormina via Piazza Armerina to view the Roman mosaics of the Villa Romana del Casale. Stay 2 nights at the Hotel Splendid (or similar).\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Valley of the Temples - Piazza Armerina - Taormina\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUundze\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_247937\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":6007,\"cityIDTo\":2455,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Erice\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Agrigento\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_246858\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}],\"meals\":[\"breakfast\",\"lunch\"]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuneA8\",\"day\":6.1,\"dayTitle\":\"Transfer: Agrigento to Taormina\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuneFN\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_246858\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":2455,\"cityIDTo\":3619,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Agrigento\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Taormina\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250552\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuneKc\",\"accommodations\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuneaL\",\"accommodation\":{\"_ref\":\"accommodation-32271\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"options\":[185182]}],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunePr\",\"city\":\"Taormina\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250552\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":7,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eVisit the highest active volcano in Europe, Mount Etna, for panoramic views. Stop at Barone di Villagrande for wine tasting at a local vineyard. Afternoon guided tour of the Taormina Amphitheatre. In the evening, enjoy a farewell dinner.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Mount Etna\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuneV6\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_246858\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":2455,\"cityIDTo\":3619,\"cityNameFrom\":\"Agrigento\",\"cityNameTo\":\"Taormina\",\"cityTo\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250552\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"transferType\":\"Road\"}],\"meals\":[\"breakfast\",\"dinner\"]},{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunefa\",\"accommodations\":[],\"cities\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUunekp\",\"city\":\"Taormina\",\"cityID\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250552\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true}}],\"day\":8,\"dayDescription\":\"\u003cp\u003eTransfer to Catania airport and fly to London with British Airways or begin your tour extension.\u003c/p\u003e\",\"dayLandOnly\":false,\"dayTitle\":\"Fly to London\",\"mapInfo\":[{\"_key\":\"uqKP1CJoSsgXdCXPUuneq4\",\"cityFrom\":{\"_ref\":\"geotree_city_250552\",\"_type\":\"reference\",\"_weak\":true},\"cityIDFrom\":3619,\