2-28T00:00:00\",\"display\":true,\"internalAir\":false,\"internalAirNotes\":null,\"note\":\"Prices are per person, double occupancy and subject to change.\",\"permit\":false,\"permitPrice\":0,\"price\":2895,\"singleSupplementPrice\":0}],\"journeyDetails\":[{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWg9\",\"description\":\"Simpler in emphasis, these itineraries typically feature 4-star or good 3-star accommodation throughout, or the best alternative elsewhere.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Standard Tour\"},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWk6\",\"description\":\"Medium pace, some  longer travel days, with uneven terrain and  longer walks requiring good fitness  and mobility.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Moderate activity level\"},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWo3\",\"description\":\"For a price quote based on alternative accommodation standards, to discuss flight options or to tailor this itinerary, please call to speak with a Cox \u0026 Kings consultant or enquire online.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":true,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Tailor-made travel\"},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWs0\",\"description\":\"Prices above are per person in Euros, based on two people sharing a twin/double-room. Single supplement available on request. Pricing is indicative and may be subject to change.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":false,\"eu\":true,\"gb\":false,\"us\":false,\"world\":false},\"title\":\"Guideline prices\"},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWvx\",\"description\":\"Prices above are per person in pounds sterling (£), based on two people sharing a twin/double-room. Single supplement available on request. Pricing is indicative and may be subject to change due to external factors such as variable flight prices.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":false,\"eu\":false,\"gb\":true,\"us\":false,\"world\":false},\"title\":\"Guideline prices\"},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWzu\",\"description\":\"Prices above are per person in Australian Dollars, based on two people sharing a twin/double-room. Single supplement available on request. Pricing is indicative and may be subject to change.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":true,\"eu\":false,\"gb\":false,\"us\":false,\"world\":false},\"title\":\"Guideline prices\"},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNX3r\",\"description\":\"Prices above are per person in United States Dollars, based on two people sharing a twin/double-room. Single supplement available on request. Pricing is indicative and may be subject to change.\",\"markets\":{\"au\":false,\"eu\":false,\"gb\":false,\"us\":true,\"world\":true},\"title\":\"Guideline prices\"}],\"lengthDays\":11,\"locations\":0,\"locationsType\":null,\"lowestPreviousPrices\":[],\"lowestPrices\":[{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWQL\",\"currency\":\"AUD\",\"price\":3595},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWUI\",\"currency\":\"EUR\",\"price\":1695},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWYF\",\"currency\":\"GBP\",\"price\":2395},{\"_key\":\"4lXD1QprlKmqniOHajNWcC\",\"currency\":\"USD\",\"price\":2895}],\"map\":\"https://stcontentprodeastus001.blob.core.windows.net/ecm/Renderings/434/P105581.svg\",\"mapJson\":\"$32\",\"maxDiscounts\":[],\"offerFlags\":{\"au\":false,\"eu\":false,\"gb\":false,\"us\":false,\"world\":false},\"offers\":[],\"overviewText\":\"Enjoy a taste of Peru on this introductory tour of some of the country's most famous sights. Discover the colonial-era wonders of Lima and Cuzco. Explore the Sacred Valley of the Incas and visit a local market and the impressive Ollantaytambo fortress. Stay overnight by the spectacular Incan city of Machu Picchu and take a boat ride on beautiful Lake Titicaca, high in the Andes.\",\"packageTypeId\":39,\"people\":[],\"slug\":{\"_type\":\"slug\",\"current\":\"tailor-made-journey/classic-peru-standard\"},\"subType\":\"Tailor-Made Journey\",\"tags\":[],\"title\":\"Classic Peru Standard\",\"type\":\"Tailor Made Day by Day\",\"year\":null},{\"A